ext\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11922155_18\">On Colored Heap Games of Sumbers</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 11</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Will_Leckie&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Will Leckie (page does not exist)\">Will Leckie</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Michael_Greenspan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Michael Greenspan (page does not exist)\">Michael Greenspan</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11922155_19\">An Event-Based Pool Physics Simulator</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 11</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jean-Pierre_Dussault&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jean-Pierre Dussault (page does not exist)\">Jean-Pierre Dussault</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jean-Fran%C3%A7ois_Landry&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jean-François Landry (page does not exist)\">Jean-François Landry</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11922155_20\">Optimization of a Billiard Player - Position Play</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 11</a></li></ul>\n<p><span id=\"Invited\"></span>\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Invited_Lectures\">Invited Lectures</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_11&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Invited Lectures\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Tony_Marsland\" title=\"Tony Marsland\">Tony Marsland</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=